name: MUSHROOM CANE CHAIR
description: The Mushroom Cane Chair is a stylish blend of modern design and natural elegance. Its distinctive mushroom-shaped backrest is beautifully crafted with cane weaving, offering both visual interest and breathability. The seat is generously cushioned for comfort, on a sturdy frame featuring subtle yet striking brass details at the base, adding a touch of luxury. The chairs legs have hand chiseled legs & back rest a rich texture that contrasts against the smooth, natural cane, creating a sophisticated juxtaposition. The brass accents at the feet subtly shine through, enhancing the overall look without overpowering the natural materials. Perfect for both contemporary and classic interiors, this chair is a refined combination of craftsmanship, comfort, and timeless style. Detailed dimensions Black Chisel

The form adds a sophisticated, modern touch to the tables, while the textured surfaces create a sense of depth and visual interest. Perfect for contemporary spaces, these tables offer both style and functionality. It strikes a perfect balance between delicacy and strength. Detailed dimensions Cast Aluminium Brass & OB Black
